                "lastUpdated": "2023-12-15T09:37:36.170000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Bill entitled an Act, in the public interest, to assist in maintaining the security of the electricity supply system in the State, and for that purpose to provide for the transfer to the western development commission of the Derrybrien wind farm; to effect the transfer of shares in Gort Windfarms Limited to the Western Development Commission; to provide for the removal of persons from certain offices positions or employment with Gort wind farms limited and provide for the appointment of persons to those offices or positions or that employment; to extinguish certain rights; to provide for the re-naming of Gort Wind Farms Limited; to provide for the transfer of the lessee’s interest in the lands at Derrybrien; to disapply certain provisions of the Companies Acts and other enactments in so far as they relate to Gort wind farms limited; to provide for the preservation of contracts; to provide for the making of regulations; and to provide for connected matters.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht, ar mhaithe le leas an phobail, chun cabhrú le slándáil an tsoláthair leictreachais sa Stát a chothabháil agus, chun na críche sin, do dhéanamh socrú maidir le Feirm Ghaoithe Dharaidh Braoin a aistriú chuig Coimisiún Forbartha an Iarthair; do dhéanamh scaireanna in <em>Gort Windfarms Limited</em> a aistriú chuig Coimisiún Forbartha an Iarthair; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le daoine a chur as oifigí, poist nó fostaíocht áirithe le <em>Gort Windfarms Limited</em> agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le daoine a cheapadh chun na n-oifigí nó na bpost nó na fostaíochta sin; do mhúchadh cearta áirithe; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le <em>Gort Windfarms Limited</em> a athainmniú; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le leas an léasaí sna tailte i nDaraidh Braoin a aistriú; do dhéanamh forálacha áirithe d’Achtanna na gCuideachtaí agus d’achtacháin eile a dhífheidhmiú a mhéid a bhaineann siad le <em>Gort Windfarms Limited</em>; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le conarthaí a choimeád ar marthain; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le rialacháin a dhéanamh; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe comhghaolmhara.</p>\n",
