                "lastUpdated": "2023-12-14T15:35:50.040000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to enable the State to participate in certain donor or trust funds established by the European Investment Bank, the Council of Europe Development Bank or the European Bank for Reconstruction and Development, and, for that purpose, to enable the State to enter into certain contribution agreements related to those funds prescribed by the Minister for Finance, and for those and other purposes to amend the European Bank for Reconstruction and Development Act 1991 and the Council of Europe Development Bank Act 2004; to enable the State to participate in the provision of exceptional macro-financial assistance by the European Union to Ukraine and, for that purpose to enable the State to enter into the guarantee agreement provided for in Article 10 of Decision (EU) 2022/1628 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 20 September 2022 and a contribution agreement as provided for in Article 7(1) of Regulation (EU) 2022/2463 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 14 December 2022; to amend section 38 of the Criminal Justice (Money Laundering and Terrorist Financing) Act 2010; and to provide for related matters.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht dá chumasú don Stát páirt a ghlacadh i gcistí deontóra nó i gcistí iontaobhais áirithe arna mbunú ag an mBanc Eorpach Infheistíochta, ag Banc Forbartha Chomhairle na hEorpa nó ag an mBanc Eorpach le haghaidh Athchóiriú agus Forbairt, agus, chun na críche sin, dá chumasú don Stát comhaontuithe ranníocaíochta áirithe a bhaineann leis na cistí sin agus a fhorordóidh an tAire Airgeadais a dhéanamh, agus, chun na gcríoch sin agus chun críoch eile, do leasú an Achta um Banc Eorpach le haghaidh Athchóiriú agus Forbairt, 1991 agus an Achta um Banc Forbartha Chomhairle na hEorpa, 2004; dá chumasú don Stát páirt a ghlacadh i soláthar cúnaimh macrairgeadais eisceachtúil ag an Aontas Eorpach don Úcráin agus, chun na críche sin, dá chumasú don Stát an comhaontú ráthaíochta dá bhforáiltear in Airteagal 10 de Chinneadh (AE) 2022/1628 ó Pharlaimint na hEorpa agus ón gComhairle an 20 Meán Fómhair 2022 a dhéanamh agus comhaontú ranníocaíochta de réir mar a fhoráiltear in Airteagal 7(1) de Rialachán (AE) 2022/2463 ó Pharlaimint na hEorpa agus ón gComhairle an 14 Nollaig 2022 a dhéanamh; do leasú alt 38 den Acht um Cheartas Coiriúil (Sciúradh Airgid agus Maoiniú Sceimhlitheoireachta), 2010; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.</p>\n",
