                "lastUpdated": "2023-12-14T09:28:51.520000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to amend the Criminal Justice (Victims of Crime) Act 2017 to permit and encourage courts to refer cases to restorative justice schemes between charge and conviction, and to dismiss charges if appropriate; to encourage courts to refer cases to restorative justice schemes between conviction and sentencing; to permit and encourage An Garda Síochána and the Director of Public Prosecutions to refer cases to restorative justice schemes between charge and court, and to review the decision to prosecute if appropriate; and to make related provisions.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú an Achta um Cheartas Coiriúil (Íospartaigh na Coireachta), 2017 chun a cheadú do chúirteanna, agus chun cúirteanna a spreagadh, cásanna a tharchur chuig scéimeanna um cheartas aisig idir tráth an chúisimh agus tráth an chiontaithe, agus cúisimh a dhíbhe, más cuí; do spreagadh cúirteanna chun cásanna a tharchur chuig scéimeanna um cheartas aisig idir tráth an chiontaithe agus gearradh na pianbhreithe; dá cheadú don Gharda Síochána agus don Stiúrthóir Ionchúiseamh Poiblí, agus dá spreagadh, cásanna a tharchur chuig scéimeanna um cheartas aisig idir tráth an chúisimh agus tráth na cúirte, agus d’athbhreithniú na breithe chun ionchúiseamh a dhéanamh, más cuí; agus do dhéanamh forálacha gaolmhara.</p>\n",
