                "lastUpdated": "2023-12-14T12:12:31.950000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to amend and extend the Social Welfare Acts; to amend the Sick Leave Act 2022 and the Workplace Relations Act 2015; to make provision for the attribution, in certain circumstances, for the purposes of the State pension (contributory), of contributions by certain persons who provide long-term care and attention to certain other persons and for the deferral, on a voluntary basis, by certain persons in certain circumstances in accessing the State pension (contributory) and, for those and other purposes, to further amend and extend the Social Welfare Acts; and to provide for related matters.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú agus do leathnú na nAchtanna Leasa Shóisialaigh; do leasú an Achta um Shaoire Bhreoiteachta, 2022 agus an Achta um Chaidreamh san Áit Oibre, 2015; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le ranníocaí ó dhaoine áirithe a sholáthraíonn cúram agus aireachas fadtéarma do dhaoine áirithe eile a chur ina leith, in imthosca áirithe, chun críocha an phinsin Stáit (ranníocach) agus maidir le daoine áirithe d’iarchur rochtain ar an bpinsean Stáit (ranníocach) ar bhonn saorálach in imthosca áirithe agus, chun na gcríoch sin agus chun críoch eile, do leasú agus do leathnú na nAchtanna Leasa Shóisialaigh tuilleadh; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.</p>\n",
