                "lastUpdated": "2023-12-12T15:49:13.050000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to provide that members of Garda personnel may operate, or cause to be operated, recording devices in certain circumstances; to provide for additional conditions regarding the operation of body-worn cameras; to provide for the circumstances in which ANPR data, which includes relevant data from relevant bodies, may be utilised by members of Garda personnel; to provide for the recording of certain telephone calls to or from the Garda Síochána and the processing thereof; to outline the circumstances in which CCTV may be installed or operated for particular purposes; to provide for authorisation by the Commissioner of the Garda Síochána for the installation and operation of CCTV by the Garda Síochána or by a local authority for those purposes; to provide for the repeal of section 38 of the Garda Síochána Act 2005 with associated transitional provisions; to provide that members of Garda personnel may, pursuant to an authorisation given by the District Court or an approval granted by an independent superior officer, process the live feed CCTV operated by a third party; to provide that a member of Garda personnel may request retained CCTV data from a third party and for failure to furnish such data to be an offence; to provide for the installation or operation of CCTV in Garda Síochána premises pursuant to an authorisation; to provide for the preparation of draft codes of practice in relation to the operation of Parts 2 to 6 and for the Minister to declare them by order to be codes of practice; to make certain provision for the admissibility of evidence; to provide for a review of operation of Part 3 and Part 6; to amend the Criminal Justice (Surveillance) Act 2009; to provide for certain offences; and to provide for related matters.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú chun go bhféadfaidh comhaltaí de phearsanra an Gharda feistí taifeadta a oibriú, nó a chur faoi deara feistí taifeadta a oibriú, in imthosca áirithe; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le coinníollacha breise i dtaobh ceamaraí éide a oibriú; do dhéanamh socrú maidir leis na himthosca ina bhféadfaidh comhaltaí de phearsanra an Gharda sonraí UAUP, lena n-áirítear sonraí iomchuí ó chomhlachtaí iomchuí, a úsáid; do dhéanamh socrú chun glaonna teileafóin áirithe ar an nGarda Síochána nó ón nGarda Síochána a thaifeadadh agus chun na glaonna teileafóin sin a phróiseáil; do thabhairt sracléiriú ar na himthosca ina bhféadfar TCI a shuiteáil nó a oibriú chun críoch áirithe; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le Coimisinéir an Gharda Síochána d’údarú don Gharda Síochána nó d’údarás áitiúil TCI a shuiteáil agus a oibriú chun na gcríoch sin; do dhéanamh socrú chun alt 38 d’Acht an Gharda Síochána, 2005 a aisghairm mar aon le socruithe idirthréimhseacha gaolmhara; do dhéanamh socrú go bhféadfaidh comhaltaí de phearsanra an Gharda, de bhun údarú arna thabhairt ag an gCúirt Dúiche nó de bhun ceadú arna dheonú ag oifigeach uachtarach neamhspleách, an TCI fotha bheo arna oibriú ag tríú páirtí a phróiseáil; do dhéanamh socrú go bhféadfaidh comhalta de phearsanra an Gharda sonraí TCI a choinnítear a iarraidh ar thríú páirtí agus gur cion é mainneachtain sonraí den sórt sin a thabhairt; do dhéanamh socrú chun TCI a shuiteáil nó a oibriú in áitreabh de chuid an Gharda Síochána de bhun údarú; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le dréacht chóid chleachtais a ullmhú i ndáil le hoibriú Chodanna 2 go 6 agus maidir leis an Aire do dhearbhú, le hordú, gur cóid chleachtais iad; do dhéanamh foráil áirithe maidir le hinghlacthacht fianaise; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le hathbhreithniú ar oibriú Chuid 3 agus Chuid 6; do leasú an Achta um Cheartas Coiriúil (Faireachas), 2009; do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh cionta áirithe; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.</p>\n",
