                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to prohibit persons from engaging in certain conduct in safe access zones, that is to say, in certain areas in and adjacent to certain healthcare premises; to make provision for enforcement in respect of engaging in conduct prohibited in such safe access zones, and to provide for offences in relation to such prohibited conduct; and to provide for matters connected therewith.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do thoirmeasc ar dhaoine gabháil d’iompar áirithe i gcriosanna rochtana sábháilte, is é sin le rá, i limistéir áirithe in áitribh cúraim sláinte áirithe agus tadhlach leo; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le forfheidhmiú i leith gabháil d’iompar a thoirmisctear i gcriosanna rochtana sábháilte den sórt sin, agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le cionta i ndáil le hiompar toirmiscthe den sórt sin; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe a bhaineann leis an méid sin.</p>\n",
