                "lastUpdated": "2023-11-09T17:20:07.440000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to provide for a process to allow for certain transactions that may present risks to the security or public order of the State to be reviewed by the Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment; to empower the Minister to require the provision of information from certain persons for reviewing, and to make decisions and take certain actions in relation to, transactions that present risks to the security or public order of the State; to provide for a process for appealing certain decisions of the Minister with due regard to the potentially sensitive nature of the subject matter of the appeal, and for those purposes to establish a panel of persons to deal with appeals against certain decisions of the Minister under this Act; to establish a panel of persons to advise the Minister in relation to certain transactions; to give further effect to Regulation (EU) 2019/452 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 19 March 2019 establishing a framework for the screening of foreign direct investments into the Union; and to provide for related matters.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le próiseas chun a cheadú don Aire Fiontar, Trádála agus Fostaíochta athbhreithniú a dhéanamh ar idirbhearta áirithe a d’fhéadfadh a bheith ina bpriacail do shlándáil nó d’ord poiblí an Stáit; do chumhachtú don Aire a cheangal ar dhaoine áirithe faisnéis a sholáthar chun athbhreithniú a dhéanamh ar idirbhearta a bheidh ina bpriacail do shlándáil nó d’ord poiblí an Stáit agus dá chumhachtú don Aire breitheanna a thabhairt agus gníomhartha áirithe a dhéanamh i ndáil le hidirbhearta den sórt sin; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le próiseas chun achomharc a dhéanamh i gcoinne breitheanna áirithe ón Aire ag féachaint go cuí d’ábhar an achomhairc a d’fhéadfadh a bheith de chineál íogair agus, chun na gcríoch sin, do bhunú painéal daoine chun déileáil le hachomhairc i gcoinne breitheanna áirithe ón Aire faoin Acht seo; do bhunú painéal daoine chun comhairle a thabhairt don Aire i ndáil le hidirbhearta áirithe; do thabhairt tuilleadh éifeachta do Rialachán (AE) 2019/452 ó Pharlaimint na hEorpa agus ón gComhairle an 19 Márta 2019 lena gcuirtear ar bun creat maidir le hinfheistíochtaí díreacha coigríche isteach san Aontas a scagadh; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.</p>\n",
