                "lastUpdated": "2023-10-26T14:02:19.900000+00:00",
                "longTitleEn": "<p>Bill entitled an Act to provide for the specific offence of spiking characterised by the administration, injection, or causation of the taking orally of a substance, knowing that the person to whom the substance is administered, injected, or caused to be taken does not consent, or being reckless as to whether the person consents, and where the perpetrator intends to overpower or sedate the person, to engage in a sexual act, cause harm, make a gain or cause a loss, or otherwise commit an offence.</p>\n",
                "longTitleGa": "<p>Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir leis an gcion sonrach arb éard é spíceáil arb é a príomhthréith substaint a thabhairt nó a instealladh, nó glacadh substainte de bhéal a chur faoi deara, i gcás gurb eol nach bhfuil an duine dá dtugtar an tsubstaint, ina n-instealltar an tsubstaint nó a gcuirtear faoi deara é nó í do ghlacadh na substainte de bhéal ag toiliú, nó go bhfuiltear meargánta i dtaobh an bhfuil an duine ag toiliú, agus go mbeartaíonn déantóir an chiona an duine a smachtú nó a thámhú, chun dul i mbun gníomh gnéasach, díobháil a dhéanamh, gnóchan a dhéanamh nó caillteanas a thabhairt, nó cion a dhéanamh ar shlí eile.</p>\n",
